ZH: 我在公园上找到一个舒适的长椅。
EN: I found a comfortable bench in the park.

ZH: 长椅上坐着一个老人。
EN: There is an old man sitting on the bench.

ZH: 公园里有很多长椅供人休息。
EN: There are many benches in the park for people to rest.

ZH: 我在长椅上看书。
EN: I am reading on the bench.

ZH: 这个长椅很脏，不想坐。
EN: This bench is dirty, I don't want to sit on it.

ZH: 公园里的长椅很漂亮。
EN: The benches in the park are beautiful.

ZH: 我在长椅上休息了一会儿。
EN: I took a rest on the bench for a while.

ZH: 长椅上的涂鸦很有意思。
EN: The graffiti on the bench is interesting.

ZH: 他在长椅上等了我半个小时。
EN: He waited for me on the bench for half an hour.

ZH: 妈妈坐在长椅上给我看故事书。
EN: Mom sat on the bench and read a storybook to me.

ZH: 来，我们坐在这个长椅上聊聊天吧。
EN: Come, let's sit on this bench and chat.

ZH: 过马路的时候，我们找到了一个长椅休息。
EN: When crossing the road, we found a bench to rest.

ZH: 公园里很多人选择坐在长椅上晒太阳。
EN: Many people in the park choose to sit on the bench to sunbathe.

ZH: 长椅旁边有个漂亮的花坛。
EN: There is a beautiful flower bed next to the bench.

ZH: 我在长椅上看到了一只可爱的小狗。
EN: I saw a cute little dog on the bench.

ZH: 长椅的颜色和公园的环境很协调。
EN: The color of the bench matches the park environment.

ZH: 我经常在长椅上等公交车。
EN: I often wait for the bus on the bench.

ZH: 长椅是铁制的，很结实。
EN: The bench is made of iron and is very sturdy.

ZH: 这个公园的长椅都很新。
EN: The benches in this park are all new.

ZH: 这个长椅可以轻松容纳三个人。
EN: This bench can easily accommodate three people.
